title: Swamy's Bakery
typeOfFood: Vegan, Indian, Macrobiotic, Organic, Raw, Western, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Bakery
description: Vegan and mostly organic food restaurant providing salads, dosas, gluten-free bread, sugar cane juice, fresh juices and smoothies, raw cakes and pastries, curries, and whole wheat pastas. Stylish atmosphere with Wi-Fi and 2nd floor roof top garden. Located opposite from sathya sai baba temple at the main road at the corner to samadhi road.
